m19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=473.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Perfect Solo Place?</span><hr size=1> <br>Here are some things you might try...<br><br>Goos In City of Mist: There is a thread here about it, there are 3 goos that are blue to 60.<br><br>HS IZ: Again, there is a thread here about this. I would not try it without epic and a symbol or aego, at least to start. I've only done it at lvl 60 with epic and spellshield.  You can bail out by leving and jumping into the basement.<br><br>Spiders and Bears in Permafrost Pit: The big problem is getting past some See-Invis Ice Giants.<br><br>Akheva: Aliens at the IZ are soloable, they run slow too!<br><br>Chardok: Not to hard to solo the IZ mobs here.<br><br>Trolls and Ogres in Neriak. Go to the Foreign Quarter Arena (first zone in). You will prob need a lot of mana for these, root and nuke, there also is not a whole lot of room.  Make sure to snare, don't let these guys run! Also root doesn't stick *really* well.<br><br>Phase Spiders in DN: There is a thread here, prob best not to try til 60 tho.<br><br>Brownies in LFay<br><br>The IZ stuff in Acrylia<br><br>Another suggestion is to go to the mage and necro boards for ideas.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uspace78.showPublicProfile?language=EN>space78</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/02 8:28:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=473.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> solo</span><hr size=1> i've tried looking around the mage boards, but most of those suggestions are out of my league. mage/necro's can take things with alot more hp's than wizards. ill try chardok first, since i'm familiar with the entrance and exit of the zone. <br>i've heard about caster mob changes, now they supposedly use higher level spells and chain cast. i would assume this would make those pesky brownies easier, since the last time i did them the only damage i took was from their melee. <br><br>thanks for the suggestions, ill go see if i can stay alive with em in mind <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=473.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=473.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=473.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=473.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=473.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=473.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=473.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email 